<p>Be sure to mark your calendars for the final major WordPress events in 2025: <a href="https://us.wordcamp.org/2025/">WordCamp US</a> (Portland, Oregon, USA). Then join us in <a href="https://europe.wordcamp.org/2026/">Kraków, Poland for WordCamp Europe 2026</a>! Also, if you want to get involved with WCEU, the call for organisers is already open for 2026. </p>



